headline: Starbucks hands Anomaly US creative duties in blow to WPP: report
summary: WPP, which only won the account in October, established a bespoke Team Starbucks unit to support the coffee chain’s turnaround plan.

headline: Three Reasons to Avoid SBUX and One Stock to Buy Instead
